00:11:42.000 --> 00:11:44.690
What developers really need as
business leaders and decision

00:11:44.690 --> 00:11:47.990
makers is data in context,
which is really information,

00:11:47.990 --> 00:11:51.560
because information can
actually empower leaders to make

00:11:51.560 --> 00:11:53.630
meaningful business
decisions that will actually

00:11:53.630 --> 00:11:55.392
result in a positive impact.

00:11:55.392 --> 00:11:57.350
TOM GRINSTED: Right, no,
